  "additional_info": "Use this style to modify Chrome's scroll bar. Especially useful on touch screen laptops, where the scrollbar is too small/thin to scroll easily. But useful for anybody.\r\n\r\nDefaults to a scrollbar 30px thick and a dark color theme. But you can customize it with your own desired width and color scheme.",
  "style_tags": [],
  "css": "/* scrollbar section */\r\n\r\n::-webkit-scrollbar{\r\n    background-color:/*[[bgcolor]]*/;\r\n    width: /*[[howwide]]*/px!important;\r\n}\r\n\r\nbody::-webkit-scrollbar{\r\n    background-color: /*[[bgcolor]]*/;\r\n}\r\n\r\n::-webkit-scrollbar-track{\r\n    background-color: /*[[bgcolor]]*/;\r\n}\r\n\r\n::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{\r\n    background-color: /*[[scrollercolor]]*/;\r\n    border-radius: /*[[justthetip]]*/px;\r\n}\r\n::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover{\r\n    background-color: /*[[hovercolor]]*/;\r\n    \r\n}\r\n::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:active{\r\n    background-color: /*[[activecolor]]*/;\r\n    \r\n}\r\n\r\n",
